subject: Dear  ,
body:
Dear  ,
Happy New Year to all of us  Welcome to the year 2024.. May the Good Lord grant completion and fulfillment to all our plans and proposals this year
May He grant answers to all our prayer requests from Him and all our pure heart desires 
May He make this year better than the previous years
And may we see the end of this year more joyous than we had seen the end of other years.... All these and more we ask of the Lord, Amen
Edward

subject: Re:   Dear  ,
body:
Dear Edward,

Thank you for your warm wishes and kind words. I hope you had a wonderful New Year as well. It's always nice to start the year with positive thoughts and aspirations. May this year bring you happiness, success, and fulfillment in all your endeavors.

Is there anything specific you are looking forward to or hoping to achieve this year? I'd love to hear more about your plans and goals.

Wishing you a fantastic year ahead!

Best wishes,
Deanna
